url: 'https://github.com/HitOdessit/ColorMixLab'
abstract: >-
  A Kotlin Multiplatform color-mixing game for Android and iOS,
  built end-to-end with AI tooling (Claude Code via Cursor and the
  Claude Code CLI). 30 levels, 15+ unlockable colors organized into
  6 random tiers, math challenges as level gating, time-windowed
  local leaderboard, particle-based completion celebration.
